287
00:21:30,750 --> 00:21:34,332
But you better post your real name
and address. Otherwise, what's the point?

288
00:21:34,485 --> 00:21:37,360
Oh, do a public dive at an Internet cafe, man!

289
00:21:39,672 --> 00:21:40,379
Do it!

